ue\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"assets/files/Printing _Périodes zodiacales et planétaires.pdf\" aria-expanded=\"false\" target=\"_blank\">Périodes Aphètiques, Vimshottari, Décenniales, Chara&nbsp;</a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"assets/files/Printing _Compatibilité en mariage selon la demeure lunaire.pdf\" aria-expanded=\"false\" target=\"_blank\">Kutas, compatibilité en mariage</a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"assets/files/Périodes aphètique selon Valens.pdf\" aria-expanded=\"false\" target=\"_blank\">Interprétation des Périodes selon V. Valens</a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"assets/files/Printing _Transits _à la grecque_.pdf\" aria-expanded=\"false\" target=\"_blank\">Textes anciens sur les Transits selon les Grecs &nbsp;</a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"RangSocial.html\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Traduction de Ptolémée \"Sur le Rang Social\" &nbsp;</a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"assets/files/75-TheOriginalLomashaSamhita-1.pdf\" aria-expanded=\"false\" target=\"_blank\">Lomasha Samhita, Original text by ancient Rishi</a></div></li><li class=\"nav-item dropdown\"><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"nav-link link dropdown-toggle\" href=\"Wvtechniques.html\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-toggle=\"dropdown-submenu\">WIN*VEGA 9&nbsp;<br></a><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"WVegaUpdates2022.html\" aria-expanded=\"false\" target=\"_blank\">Latest Updates,&nbsp; 2022<br></a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"WV7Intro.html\" target=\"_blank\">Win*Vega Installation&nbsp; &nbsp;(fr)<br></a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\"dropdown-item text-primary\" href=\"WVPresent.html\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Win*Vega Présentation &nbsp; &nbsp;(fr)</a><a data-app-btn=\"true\" class=\